data.title: Expense
data.meta_description: Expense - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document appears to be a list of expenses incurred between February 2013 and October 2013 categorized by date, item, place, category, quantity and amount. Some key expenses include electricity, tuition fees, medical expenses, household items, food, transportation and entertainment. The largest expenses are a home loan, personal loan and payment for a laptop. The document provides a detailed breakdown of expenses over a 10 month period across various categories.
